  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin rooms</strong> are around 15m² sleeping two and have an en-suite, and balcony with lake view.</p>
<p><strong>Triple rooms</strong> are around 20m² sleeping two and have an en-suite, and balcony with lake view. </p>
<p>Please note that rooms are refreshed on request.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Most rooms have a view of the lake</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Hairdryers (on request)</li>
<li>Private bathrooms with separate toilet</li>
<li>Beds can be made up as double or twin</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
